# Normalize line endings to LF for all text files on every platform.
#
# Git auto-detects text vs. binary; detected-text files are stored and checked
# out with LF regardless of a contributor's core.autocrlf setting. This keeps
# embedded templates and golden testdata byte-identical across Linux, macOS, and
# Windows so the renderer golden tests remain deterministic.
* text=auto eol=lf
